cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper deals with combining deep convolutional neural networks and Gaussian processes for action recognition, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of distributed Gaussian processes and the Product of Experts framework may also relate to the categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and statistical learning (cs.SD).
